<plot>In this remake of two previous shorts (and also uses footage from both), Andy, the new Professor of Psychiatry at an All-Girl College, gets involved in the chase of a bandit, wearing a nightshirt, who has been robbing the campus dormitories. He corners him but, in the mêlée, the co-eds mistake him for the crook.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?423594</url></doc>
